                <b>Handmade Skichairs:</b><br />
                Handmade Skichairs, complete with matching ottoman, are the finest Adirondack style chairs available.  Skichairs are 100% handmade with five-quarter inch Port Orford Cedar, the finest most durable material for outdoor use, and assembled with stainless steel fasteners.  Skichairs can be made from Snow or Water skis, Hockey Sticks, Wake boards, Snow Boards, Base Ball Bats and Golf Clubs! Size: Height 40", Length 38", Width 33", Seat Height 15".  Ottoman: Height 15", Length 24", Width 19". Total weight of chair and ottoman: 55lbs.
                <br /><br />
                <b>Benches:</b><br />
                Benches and Table/Seats are made entirely of recycled products and utilize recycled skis, boards and Hockey sticks.  The legs are made from recycled plastics and weigh 30 lbs and 60 lbs/set.  The recycled plastic legs are available in black.  Part of the fun of owning your own Skichair or Bench is designing the look you want.  You can select from our tremendous stock of over 100,000 skis and boards and 5,000 Hockey sticks.  We will provide you with best visual presentation and Brand you want! 
